<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-07-06T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-07-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="83" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d83">
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <head><persName type="from">Mr. Perry</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Seward</persName></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 129.]</seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">United States Consulate</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Tunis,</hi></placeName>
                                <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-07-06"><hi rend="italic">July</hi> 6, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir :</hi> Since my last despatch the general health
                            of this city has decidedly improved, though the accounts from the
                            interior of the regency are far from being satisfactory. The cholera has
                            appeared in very many villages, among some wandering tribes and in the
                            army of the Bey, though it is by no means so destructive as in former
                            years.</p>
                        <p rend="center">* * * * * *</p>
                        <p>I have the honor to be, very respectfully, your obedient servant,</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>AMOS PERRY.</signed>
                        </closer>
                        <postscript>
                            <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D. C.</hi></p>
                        </postscript>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>